  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The process of enhancing functional capacity of the individual in anticipation of an upcoming
      stressor has been termed &quot;prehabilitation&quot;. In the present pilot trial, the impact of a
      multimodal prehabilitation intervention composed of exercise, nutritional supplement and
      psychological well-being begun in the preoperative period will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
